from work. I onyl wenty on now because if I didn't I would be so far

gonna do a quick thing on Fliq and Bronco.)

Now that they have Fliq's permission, they headed straight for The 
Ark's scanning systems. They tried to use them, but to no avail.

"Damn Preds," said Bronco, "I can't wait until this thing is rebuilt. 
What do we do now?"

"When we scanned from the Cybertronian Fire, it said that all the 
debris was in the next sector over. We'll just go there and cover the 
area with our short range sensors."

Fliq and Bronco changed to Bot mode, and took off with their jets 
blazing.)

(See you all tomorrow.)
